#: ../../source/openshift_configuration.rst:25
msgid "The controller links to OpenShift itself in order to facilitate scaling up and down without requiring you to manually execute the playbook (to bring up new nodes) or run management commands in the shell (to take nodes offline purposefully). You can configure the controller Deployment once the system is up to add more or remove extra controller Pods."
